```plantuml
@startuml ashavijit_Face-Find

actor User
participant "Django View" as DV
participant "Model" as M
participant "Azure Face API" as API
participant "Email Service" as ES

User -> DV: Access missing person list page
DV -> M: Query MissingPerson
M --> DV: Return list of missing persons
DV -> User: Render list view

User -> DV: Access report person form
DV -> M: Create ReportedPerson entry
DV -> API: Generate face ID and match
API --> DV: Return potential matches
alt Matches Found
    DV -> ES: Send email notification
    ES --> DV: Notification sent
end
DV -> User: Render success page

User -> DV: Access update missing person form
DV -> M: Update MissingPerson
DV -> API: Update face ID
API --> DV: Acknowledgement
DV -> User: Render update success page

@enduml
```